Simple snowflakes and fractal curves generator, done in js + html5canvas
todo-list (future features):
- user should choose fractal curve initializer/generator himself
- add possibilities to customize colors and background of drawings
- add more kinds of snowflakes, not only "4-axis of symmetry"-based
- add possibility to save drawed picture
- draw snowflakes and curves in the center of canvas, without going over the edge

